        <name>bt_hrs_cb_register</name>
        <param>
          <type>struct <ref refid="structbt__hrs__cb" kindref="compound">bt_hrs_cb</ref> *</type>
          <declname>cb</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Heart rate service callback register. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function will register callbacks that will be called in certain events related to Heart rate service.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>cb</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to callbacks structure. Must point to memory that remains valid until unregistered.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 on success </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>-EINVAL in case <computeroutput>cb</computeroutput> is NULL </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
