        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Heart rate service callback unregister. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function will unregister callback from Heart rate service.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>cb</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to callbacks structure</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 on success </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>-EINVAL in case <computeroutput>cb</computeroutput> is NULL </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>-ENOENT in case the <computeroutput>cb</computeroutput> was not found in registered callbacks </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
